divs: Sighting DetailsI was leaving General Mills my place of employment and when pulling out of the parking lot notice like five or six head light in a row over the rio grande are of town hovering when pulling out of work noticed the lights under the bridge getting closer and brighter and then the were gone when I got near my house where the elevation is higher there were no lights to be seen.
